p.k: Gumball and Darwin spice up their friendship by introducing a third best friend... / Gumball has to save Mr Robinson’s life during Elmore’s Senior Talent Show! / Gumball tries to save Darwin from being kissed by a girl. / Principal Brown tries to “fix” Gumball’s dysfunctional family. / Sarah, the new kid in school, is Gumball and Darwin's number one, slightly obsessive, fan. / Whilst Gumball and Darwin make fun of Mum and Dad for being old, their voices start to break. / The Wattersons are surprised to discover that their past actions have consequences. / The life of the background objects of Elmore are shown in a series of short skits. / The Watterson kids come up with a fool-proof plan.
